cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.MM

The paper presents a machine learning-based approach for predicting knee osteoarthritis progression using radiographic data and clinical examination results. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the use of medical data and patient history suggests a potential fit for computational biology (cs.CE). Finally, the use of multiple modalities (radiographic and clinical data) could also suggest a fit for multimedia (cs.MM).
